  <titles>
    <title type="display">Arctic Refuge Protection Act</title>
    <title type="short" as="introduced">Arctic Refuge Protection Act</title>
    <title type="official" as="introduced">To amend Public Law 115-97 (commonly known as the Tax Cuts and Jobs Act) to repeal the Arctic National Wildlife Refuge oil and gas program, and to preserve the Arctic coastal plain of the Arctic National Wildlife Refuge, Alaska, as wilderness in recognition of its extraordinary natural ecosystems and for the permanent good of present and future generations of Americans.</title>
